data.description: Located on a quiet cul-du-sac this thoughtfully designed home boasts a plethora of features that cater to both comfort and style.  Upon entering, you're greeted by an inviting living space adorned with recessed lighting, crown molding, and plantation shutters throughout, creating an ambiance of sophistication. The central air and heating ensure year-round comfort, while the cozy fireplace in the living room becomes the perfect focal point for chilly evenings.  The chef's dream kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, subway tile backsplash, and a convenient pot filler, making culinary endeavors a joy. The farm-style sink, coupled with a large kitchen island that seamlessly opens up into the living room, creates a perfect setting for both casual family meals and entertaining guests.  The home boast 3 bedrooms 2 baths and a bonus room perfect for the use of a den/family room.  One of the standout features of this property is the environmentally conscious addition of solar panels, providing an eco-friendly and cost-efficient energy solution along with a alkaline water system and water softener. The home also features a 2 car garage and charging station for electric car enthusiasts.  Venture outside to the backyard oasis, where you'll find a perfect blend of relaxation and entertainment. The well-maintained backyard is ideal space for outdoor gatherings and al fresco dining.  Conveniently located near attractive amenities such as parks, schools, shopping centers, while offering easy access to major highways and public transportation.  Don't miss the chance to call this exceptional property home.
